divs: Sighting Detailsone day about 2 years ago me and my friend were in my backyard on my trampoline. my friend noticed some weird thing in the sky not to high up a less high than planes normally fly. it looked weird so he told me . hes like "dude whats that? ". so i looked and at first i thought it was a plane but it had no wings and what made it really creepy was that it make no sound at all. so i said "its just a plane but... i don't know its not making any sound and doesn't have wings...?". we watched it for a few seconds before i thought of the idea and went to get my cell phone (moto Razr) to take a picture of it. after i turned the camera on i aimed the phone between 2 branches in the tree were i saw the UFO but my screen showed nothing so i moved it around zooming in and out trying to find it but it wouldn't show up on screen! i saw it with my bare eye though but it would not show up on my camera ! A while trying to find the ship on my phone camera for about 20 seconds with no luck it disappeared behind the view of the house out of our view.
